{"id": 2390, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于“过更环保的生活”这件事，你都遇到过哪些障碍？", "description": "感觉自己已经很注意了，怎么周末收拾的时候又是垃圾一大堆呢？（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 8808, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180606162641TczNS1sa0tCMmXiI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-18T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4313, "title": "关于“过更环保的生活”这件事，你都遇到过哪些障碍？", "content": "关于“过更环保的生活”这件事，你都遇到过哪些障碍？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 285497, "content": "买饮料提出用自己的杯子，被店员拒绝", "image": "img/option/option/20180607170310sZfUlY1HbupEh9Q4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285500, "content": "买完菜，摊主热情地说“多给你套几个袋子”", "image": "img/option/option/20180607170337Nx9kV3I8TMst2UFO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285790, "content": "网购越来越多，包装常常至少三层", "image": "img/option/option/20180607170347K1uGaZSUQ4EzVq0N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285792, "content": "出门需要自带杯子、购物袋等太多东西，经常忘记", "image": "img/option/option/20180607170057zZqiEoyLkdOAR1s9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285793, "content": "精心地把垃圾分类，最后扔掉之后被收到一个车里", "image": "img/option/option/20180611140904OzKpeS50YIltV7aZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285794, "content": "总有一些不知道该扔哪儿的东西，比如废电池、过期药", "image": "img/option/option/20180611141452Xq036amrHKIDwkBT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285795, "content": "点外卖每次都选不需要餐具但还是会送餐具", "image": "img/option/option/20180611141633sflDEvMzNSPiIbxZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285796, "content": "用旧的衣服、电器卖掉麻烦，扔掉可惜", "image": "img/option/option/20180611142457A1wOY6GZWzhjSCHs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}